COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 305, L.D. 451
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment changes the definition of "solar energy development" to except from
33 the requirements of the bill solar energy systems with a nameplate capacity of 100 kilowatts
44 or less that are collocated with a residential customer. The amendment also adds an
55 appropriations and allocations section.
